     <td class="lower">
       <p class="style4">The <strong>Retail Fraud Report</strong> is a merchant risk management tool that works by helping to make the best decisions from available data, reducing manual reviews, streamlining orders and managing claims.</p>
       <p class="style4">The report evaluates high-risk patterns found during address and identity verification, and summarizes all results in a single three-digit score (<strong>Chargeback Defender Identity Score</strong>) in order to help retailers best evaluate the risk of a given transaction. With this score and report, retailers can focus on the subset of accounts that contain the majority of potential losses.</p>
       <p class="style4">The Retail Fraud Report is priced at $1.00 per report. This price is exclusive of any applicable discounts or special price plans.</p>
	   <p align="center" class="style4 style14">
        <span class="style4 style14">For more information please contact your LexisNexis Account Representative, or call Customer Support at 866.858.7246.</span></p>
